 Clinical evidence More than 100 patients have already underwent an nCLE procedure, in the past studies.

 A first feasibility study enabled to define the final type of probe which would fit into a EUSFNA needle, and the INSPECT study enabled to define interpretation criteria on the micro-structure of pancreatic cysts.

 Less data is available on pancreatic masses and lymph nodes, except for a few images done in the first feasibility study.

